{"tid":1956223,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"密碼真係只有用「中文密碼」，先安全。推廣使用中文密碼，刻不容緩","createTime":"2020-04-03T04:57:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T05:49:32.000Z","uid":149978,"like":11,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0778769f8b3baca5f5d50a5dd9e475d7df65989c","tid":1956223,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T04:57:34.000Z","msg":"前提係要用：Full Disk Encryption<br />\n用lock唔用encrypt，普通軟件可以好快繞過你密碼再改。<br />\n<br />\n英文密碼唔係唔安全，但要夠長。<br />\n<br />\n中文密碼堅安全<br />\n當你有1000個常用中文字，6個中文字密碼<br />\n1000^6=10^18<br />\n電腦每秒撞10億次，要破都要用10億秒（31年）<br />\n7個中文字密碼<br />\n1000^6=10^18<br />\n電腦每秒撞100億次，要破都要用1000億秒（3100年）"},{"pid":"301d5151008393ea61013e29e68dad2c3deeab81","tid":1956223,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T04:58:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前提係要用：Full Disk Encryption<br />\n用lock唔用encrypt，普通軟件可以好快繞過你密碼再改。<br />\n<br />\n英文密碼唔係唔安全，但要夠長。<br />\n<br />\n中文密碼堅安全<br />\n當你有1000個常用中文字，6個中文字密碼<br />\n1000^6=10^18<br />\n電腦每秒撞10億次，要破都要用10億秒（31年）<br />\n7個中文字密碼<br />\n<strong>1000^7=10^21</strong><br />\n電腦每秒撞100億次，要破都要用1000億秒（3100年）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n修正"},{"pid":"3113879a4734951d81e888ec5ec2bf5b0feb4a73","tid":1956223,"uid":38405,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T05:00:15.000Z","msg":"Errrr"},{"pid":"169aad59f95638df04b04b1e5fa385aa0cc40a10","tid":1956223,"uid":7125,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T05:30:47.000Z","msg":"但係大家要真係改啲難撞既密碼<br />\n<br />\n唔係9撞光復香港之類既我估都開到幾成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d02b725cdb8a87debc0819aa3a19b1fcdfe4eb6","tid":1956223,"uid":2590,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T05:53:37.000Z","msg":"其實用中文字入密碼都係兌返做byte code先<br />\n個密碼只要夠長既話英中忟中文冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2fd5a0a390e5e4c32f47d85c3daf